{"id": "art-25150", "label": "Art. 25150", "title": "Art. 25150", "slug": "art-25150", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1681172098\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1433\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1681172098\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>50</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1712233379\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1432\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1712233379\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În termen de 45 de zile de la data efectu&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> proiectului de transformare,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>47</sup>,\norice creditor a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span> este\nanterioar&#259; acestei date <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nescadent&#259;\nla aceast&#259; dat&#259;, care este <span class=SpellE>nemul&#355;umit</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> acordate prin proiectul de\ntransformare, notific&#259; societatea pentru acordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>\nadecvate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1342717459\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1431\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1342717459\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În termen de 15 zile de la împlinirea termenului\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1), societatea transmite creditorului oferta privind\nacordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1253859589\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1430\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1253859589\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care creditorul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1)\nnu consider&#259; adecvate <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> acordate\nde societate, se poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> pentru\nobligarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> la acordarea de <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> adecvate, dac&#259; creditorul <span\nclass=SpellE>dovede&#351;te</span> c&#259; transformarea, în mod rezonabil,\nafecteaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;ansele</span> de acoperire a <span\nclass=SpellE>crean&#355;ei</span>. <span class=SpellE>Garan&#355;iile</span>\nsunt acordate sub <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca transformarea\ns&#259; produc&#259; efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1971816258\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1429\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1971816258\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cererea se depune, în termen de 3 luni de la data\nefectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>47</sup>, la oficiul\nregistrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> de la sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul transform&#259;rii,\ncare, în termen de 3 zile de la data depunerii, o <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîn registru <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> o înainteaz&#259; tribunalului în\na c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. La cerere se anexeaz&#259; dovada\nnotific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în vederea\nconstituirii de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, oferta <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nHot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este executorie <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> este supus&#259; numai apelului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1939515596\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1428\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1939515596\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Cererea creditorului se judec&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu\nprec&#259;dere. Dac&#259; sunt formulate mai multe cereri, acestea se\nconexeaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_954231449\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1427\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_954231449\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Certificatul prealabil transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere poate fi emis numai dac&#259; societatea prezint&#259; dovezi\nprivind constituirea <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span> potrivit\nproiectului de transformare transfrontalier&#259; sau ca urmare a\nnotific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ori potrivit\nhot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2001820670\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1426\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2001820670\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nromân&#259;, ca <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> a statului de\nplecare, este <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i> aplicabil&#259;\ncererilor creditorilor formulate potrivit alin. (1), iar tribunalul în a\nc&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul transform&#259;rii\nare <span class=SpellE>competen&#355;a</span> <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ion&#259;rii</span>\nlor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_632878332\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1425\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_632878332\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Pe o perioad&#259; de 2 ani de la data la care produce\nefecte transformarea transfrontalier&#259;, orice cerere a oric&#259;rui\ncreditor care <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> o <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>\nanterioar&#259; datei efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nproiectului de transformare la acea dat&#259;, în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu acea <span\nclass=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>, poate fi adresat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> în a c&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span>\nteritorial&#259; a avut sediul social societatea care s-a transformat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1530264852\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1424\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1530264852\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 172 alin. (1) lit. d), <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (1)-(8) sunt aplicabile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>"}